{"tid":1398042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（忽發奇想）不合作運動，起身屌閪啦！！！","createTime":"2019-08-02T16:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T16:51:32.000Z","uid":278029,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d82e8508732f0e8c5b3096e2e596218e4e0ce9df","tid":1398042,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:15:50.000Z","msg":"大家係形形色色嘅營會都聽過依句口號，提各位營友早起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 適逢ocamp 季節又到，各大專soc 都研究點樣社運與ocamp 並存嘅時候，小弟又覺得依種提人起身、守望相助嘅風氣理應推廣開去，好令營會中嘅良好傳統係本港推而廣之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可能諗，邊度有需要呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警察宿舍就最需要，警察救急扶危、儆惡懲奸，依排ot 得咁辛苦，一定好難起身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都唔應該因而耽誤duty，大家要盡良好公民責任，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4點左右好係宿舍樓下大叫「起身屌閪啦」，提醒宿舍入面嘅警察起身</span></span>，miss 咗間期就唔好啦。"},{"pid":"ec82b645ed1cae18f71d9cf6d4d1549c407aacc7","tid":1398042,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"246e8002d58141f48b689a5e2028a4f626afc257","tid":1398042,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80174f0d7a321631d492352fad1bfd657fdaccfe","tid":1398042,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a09b1da41a4148f88e464759769ee3078f744b8b","tid":1398042,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"8e87f3776c0ddc20ae4e79854cc2f3903ce4010b","tid":1398042,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"f746fb738fd834ef6ca7ac14f5873a3c2acf9bd5","tid":1398042,"uid":278029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"fdbbae146da0c05f074b309a